For development ...

To run a 0.25.x puppet client:

# install ruby, openssl libs for ruby
# install rubygems
# install puppet and facter gems
# run with something like:

env RUBYLIB=/var/lib/gems/1.8/gems/puppet-0.25.0/lib/:/var/lib/gems/1.8/gems/facter-1.5.6/lib/ /var/lib/gems/1.8/gems/puppet-0.25.0/sbin/puppetd --test


To run puppetca run it with vardir and ssldir options:
puppetca --vardir puppet/var --ssldir puppet/var/ssl/ ...
